title: San Diego/Downtown
name: USS Midway Aircraft Carrier Museum
price: $19 adults, $16 seniors, $15 students, $10 military/youth, children 5 and under and active military free
content: Take a self-guided tour of the USS Midway (CV-41), a former aircraft carrier of the US Navy. The Midway is home to a collection of former naval aircraft housed on her expansive flight deck. Guided tours and displays offer a unique look into the life aboard and of a powerful old warhorse.
